{"tid":1118674,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"當年梁榮忠車震偷食， 唧牙膏玩到佢變世紀賤男，至今仍然未能翻身","createTime":"2019-04-21T13:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T06:11:03.000Z","uid":43785,"like":494,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa2002bb01d16d22e1d53a2e0033de3d59d1850","tid":1118674,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"明明喺tvb有男主角做，<br />\n當年梁榮忠偷食，玩到佢變世紀賤男，至今仍然未能翻身。 痴埋左鄰右李都搞佢唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係個女嘅事後依然有拍tvb劇，而且一套接一套。 <br />\n香港人好善忘， 朱慧敏唔使一年就已經俾香港人忘記咗啦。<br />\n<br />\n相信黃心穎，不用下年已經可以繼續做心穎bb"},{"pid":"164c570727cd805af61e7e632dee97c1e277714d","tid":1118674,"uid":43785,"like":525,"dislike":7,"score":518,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KH2bMUC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKH2bMUC.jpg&h=b888f047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f7COO7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7COO7X.jpg&h=fac40a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃心穎不妨學下朱慧敏拍親戲都做淫婦做第三者，tvb就可以繼續用你。<br />\n<br />\n唔怕啦反正李佳芯之前一直都係做第三者， 狐狸精。<br />\n<br />\n當眾畀個男主角打幾巴， 喊得慘啲好似鍾嘉欣咁， 觀眾睇得痛快再下年可以爭女主角了。"},{"pid":"af334c1500dfdfc0b49e1bebb55c06849431aa64","tid":1118674,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T03:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edb1d68f69c15b13a412e9fd63ada9606f0dd90","tid":1118674,"uid":4811,"like":795,"dislike":6,"score":789,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"條女而家搞嗰個係鄭秀文老公，應該好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69314ceca70d8703579027fc72cb90701607a10a","tid":1118674,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":177,"score":-173,"quote":{"pid":"7edb1d68f69c15b13a412e9fd63ada9606f0dd90","tid":1118674,"uid":4811,"like":795,"dislike":6,"score":789,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20